------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RUNSPEC
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DIMENS
 6 5 7 /

OIL
WATER
GAS
DISGAS
VAPOIL

METRIC

START
 10 'OCT' 2018 /

--
GRIDOPTS
'YES'		0 / 


EQLDIMS
 1 1*  25 /


--
REGDIMS
-- max. ntfip  nmfipr  max. nrfreg   max. ntfreg
   1          4       1*            1*    /

--
--
WELLDIMS
--max.well  max.con/well  max.grup  max.w/grup
